###############################################
# TEST SCENARIOS
###############################################

### Test Scenario 1: Complete Invoice Lifecycle
# 1. Create invoice -> 2. Send to client -> 3. Record partial payment -> 4. Record final payment

### Test Scenario 2: Invoice from Quotation Flow
# 1. Create quotation -> 2. Accept quotation -> 3. Convert to invoice -> 4. Process payment

### Test Scenario 3: Invoice from Proforma Invoice Flow
# 1. Create PI -> 2. Accept PI -> 3. Convert to invoice -> 4. Process payment

### Test Scenario 4: Overdue Invoice Management
# 1. Create invoice with past due date -> 2. Check overdue list -> 3. Send reminder -> 4. Apply late fee

### Test Scenario 5: Bulk Operations
# 1. Create multiple invoices -> 2. Bulk mark some as paid -> 3. Bulk delete draft invoices

###############################################
# ERROR TESTING
###############################################

### Test invalid invoice creation (missing required fields)
POST {{baseUrl}}/invoices
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoiceTitle": "Test Invoice"
  // Missing required fields: clientId, date, dueDate, items
}

### Test payment amount exceeding balance
POST {{baseUrl}}/invoices/{{invoiceId}}/record-payment
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 999999,
  "method": "cash"
}

### Test invalid status transition
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/invoices/{{invoiceId}}/status
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "invalid_status"
}

### Test duplicate invoice number (should be handled automatically)
POST {{baseUrl}}/invoices
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientId": "{{clientId}}",
